reset_auctions_to_under_offer

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
reset_auctions_to_under_offer -  This function runs down the list of current auctions and makes sure they  are all registered as "Under Offer" so if for some reason they are not,  they won't be put up for sale again.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void reset_auctions_to_under_offer()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/real_estate_auction.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function runs down the list of current auctions and makes sure they 
are all registered as "Under Offer" so if for some reason they are not, 
they won't be put up for sale again.

.EP

